message.body: I'm returning to boston today!!! I want to see you! I had the most Lana del Rey time ever in philadelphia. So many motorcycle rides! What's your week look like?
I hope you, the belle of the town, had a ball in boston the past few weeks.
I am going back to Istanbul tomorrow. We were at Rochester for the new years eve. It was great!
Glad you enjoyed it too.
Dam u girl!
Well are you doing anything other than Daniel Tonight
You are gonna miss me : )
Also I ended things with Hannibal so you and your man should set me up with someone so we can double date
I am so going to miss you!!!!
I wished you had been apart of my adventures in Philadelphia
You would have had the best time
I don't think we are the best people to set you up a date : ) He is working but he will come to my place afterwards. I may not be able to go out tonigh. I am sorry. Why are you coming back already?
I have work stuff to do starting tomorrow. I figured you wouldn't be able to go out tonight oh well. When do you get back? You excited to see your niece?
Yes a lot!!
I ll back in two weeks. Not such a long time.
Well have a great time!! Yay I'm Glad ill get to see you soon
Wait when do classes start
I have no clue just assumed we didn't have another two weeks off
That's awesome
21st or 22nd I guess. I will be back on 20th.
Yay
